A Quick note : Solution for avoid admin password while connecting to new WiFi for standard user

create file new file : /var/lib/polkit-1/localauthority/50-local.d/10-network-manager.pkla with below content note: here in second line modify userame with the actual one
 
touch /var/lib/polkit-1/localauthority/50-local.d/10-network-manager.pkla
 
Add one or more policies...
[Let standard Users modify system settings for network]
Identity=unix-user:vvdn
Action=org.freedesktop.NetworkManager.settings.modify.system
ResultAny=no
ResultInactive=no
ResultActive=yes



Experimental : Try this too 
==========================
Identity=unix-group:netdev
===========================
